<i>noun</i>: 혼탁 [혼ː탁], 오염 [오ː염], 악덕 [악떡], 비리 [비ː리], 부패상 [부ː패상], 부패 [부ː패], 부정부패 [부정부패] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>혼탁 [혼ː탁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. turbidity; muddiness</dd><br>
<dd>더러운 물질이 섞여 깨끗하지 못하고 흐림.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being muddy, not clear, with a filthy substance added.</dd><br>
<dd>2. corruption; depravity</dd><br>
<dd>정치, 도덕 등의 사회 현상이 어지럽고 깨끗하지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a social phenomenon involving politics or morality is characterized by disorder and impurity.</dd><br>
<dt>오염 [오ː염]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pollution; contamination</dd><br>
<dd>더러운 상태가 됨.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being polluted.</dd><br>
<dd>2. corruption</dd><br>
<dd>순수함이 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The disappearance of pureness.</dd><br>
<dt>악덕 [악떡]</dt><br>
<dd>vice; immorality; corruption</dd><br>
<dd>부도덕하고 나쁜 마음이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>An immoral, bad intention or behavior.</dd><br>
<dt>비리 [비ː리]</dt><br>
<dd>irregularity; corruption</dd><br>
<dd>올바르지 않은 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act that is not morally right.</dd><br>
<dt>부패상 [부ː패상]</dt><br>
<dd>corrupt situation; corruption</dd><br>
<dd>정치, 사상, 의식 등이 정의롭지 못한 쪽으로 빠져든 상태나 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A state or situation in which politics, ideology, awareness, etc., have become immoral.</dd><br>
<dt>부패 [부ː패]</dt><br>
<dd>1. decomposition</dd><br>
<dd>단백질이나 지방 등이 미생물의 작용에 의하여 썩는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>The decomposition of protein, fat, etc., through the action of microorganisms.</dd><br>
<dd>2. corruption</dd><br>
<dd>정치, 사상, 의식 등이 정의롭지 못한 쪽으로 빠져드는 것.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which politics, ideology, consciousness, etc., becomes immoral.</dd><br>
<dt>부정부패 [부정부패]</dt><br>
<dd>corruption</dd><br>
<dd>도덕적으로 바르거나 깨끗하지 못함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being not morally right or clean.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>